<plot>It's open season for hunting, and Rocky the Mountain Lion takes refuge from gunfire by sneaking into a cabin owned by Elmer Fudd. Elmer doesn't realize Rocky is posing as one of the stuffed heads hanging on his wall, even though Rocky steals Elmer's steak, tobasco sauce and all. Elmer inadvertantly subjects Rocky to cruel mental punishment as an object for target practice. Rocky is happy to leave when he overhears Elmer learning by phone that hunting season is over!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?652269</url></doc>
